title: AHS: DOUBLE FEATURE Episode 3 Preview Breakdown & Theories! - "Thirst"

comment:
What do you think will happen in episode 3? Not sure if I'll be doing preview breakdowns for every episode, but if you guys like them I'll try to do them.

Check out my episode 1 & 2 breakdown video here: https://youtu.be/AbOBLHPTgUI

Thanks so much- this seems like the best season in quite a while already. Poor Alma took the pill😮
